Package: eudev
Architecture: linux-any
Pre-Depends: debconf (>= 1.4.69) | debconf-2.0
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libeudev1 (= ${binary:Version})
Conflicts: hotplug, udev
Breaks: systemd
Provides: udev
Description: Alternative /dev/ and hotplug management daemon
 eudev is a fork of systemd with the aim of isolating udev
 from any particular flavor of system initialization.
 .
 This package contains the daemon which dynamically creates
 and removes device nodes from /dev/, handles hotplug events
 and loads drivers at boot time.

Package: libeudev1
Section: libs
Architecture: linux-any
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: libudev1
Breaks: systemd
Provides: libudev1
Description: Alternative device information shared library
 eudev is a fork of systemd with the aim of isolating udev
 from any particular flavor of system initialization.
 .
 This package contains the library which provides access to
 udev device information.

Package: libeudev-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: linux-any
