Conflicts: libudev-dev
Breaks: systemd
Provides: libudev-dev
Description: libeudev development files
 eudev is a fork of systemd with the aim of isolating udev
 from any particular flavor of system initialization.
 .
 This package contains the files needed for developing applications that
 use libeudev.

Package: libgeudev-1.0-0
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: linux-any
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: libgudev-1.0-0
Breaks: systemd
Conflicts: libgudev-1.0-0
Description: GObject-based wrapper library for eudev's libudev
 eudev is a fork of systemd with the aim of isolating udev
 from any particular flavor of system initialization.
 .
 This package contains the library which eases using eudev's
 version of libudev for programs that use GObject.

